0.2.98

The first line of this file is the version number of makediary.  This
number must match the number in setup.py.

Everything else is ignored.

*** When changing the version number here, don't forget to also change:

- setup.py.

- makediary/makediary.py.

- makediary/DotCalendar.py.

- makediary/PaperSize.py.

- makediary/__init__.py.

- man/makediary.1.txt, including the copyright expiry date.

- debian/changelog.

- The version numbers in ~/bin/make-makediary-www and
  ~/bin/export-makediary-to-burst.  ??

- The version numbers in the web page.

